###Collection: professionalAvailabilities

Purpose: Stores individual time slots indicating when a professional is potentially available for work assignments. This collection facilitates matching professionals with employer needs.
Document ID: availabilityId (Unique ID generated by Firestore)
Fields:

professionalProfileId: String
Description: Reference to the document ID in the professionalProfiles collection.
Indexed: Yes.
userId: String
Description: Reference to the users document ID associated with the professional profile (for permissions/management).
Indexed: Yes.
startTime: Timestamp
Description: The exact date and time when the availability period begins (UTC).
Indexed: Yes (Essential for time-based queries).
endTime: Timestamp
Description: The exact date and time when the availability period ends (UTC).
Indexed: Yes (Essential for time-based queries).
status: String
Description: Current state of this availability slot.
Enum: 'available', 'booked', 'unavailable', 'pending_confirmation'
Indexed: Yes.
jobTypes: Array&lt;String>
Description: List of standardized job roles the professional is available for during this specific slot (e.g., ['pharmacist', 'pharma_assistant']). Should align with roles defined elsewhere.
Indexed: Yes (Array contains).
locationPreference: Map
Description: Defines the geographical area where the professional is available during this slot.
Fields:
type: String Enum ('anywhere_in_canton', 'specific_address', 'radius', 'remote_ch')
canton: String (Required if type is 'anywhere_in_canton', e.g., 'GE')
address: Map (Required if type is 'specific_address', format: { street, number, postalCode, city, canton, country: 'CH' })
centerGeoPoint: GeoPoint (Required if type is 'radius', Firestore GeoPoint)
radiusKm: Number (Required if type is 'radius')
Indexed: Yes (on canton, potentially GeoPoint if using geoqueries).
minHourlyRate: Number (Optional)
Description: Minimum acceptable gross hourly rate in CHF for this slot.
bookedDetails: Map (Optional, relevant if status is 'booked' or 'pending_confirmation')
Description: Information about the need or contract this availability is linked to.
Fields:
needId: String (Reference to employerNeeds)
contractId: String (Reference to contracts)
notes: String (Optional)
Description: Private notes for the professional regarding this availability slot.
createdAt: Timestamp
Description: When this availability record was created.
lastUpdatedAt: Timestamp
Description: When this availability record was last modified.

