###Collection: employerNeeds

Purpose: Stores specific staffing requests (shifts, openings) posted by employers. This collection is matched against professionalAvailabilities.
Document ID: needId (Unique ID generated by Firestore)
Fields:

employerProfileId: String
Description: Reference to the document ID in the employerProfiles collection.
Indexed: Yes.
postedByUserId: String
Description: Reference to the users document ID of the employer representative who created this need.
Indexed: Yes.
status: String
Description: Current state of this staffing need.
Enum: 'open', 'pending_assignment', 'filled', 'cancelled', 'expired'
Indexed: Yes.
jobTitle: String
Description: Specific title for this position/shift (e.g., "Weekend Morning Pharmacist").
jobType: String
Description: Standardized job category (e.g., 'pharmacist', 'nurse_critical_care', 'medical_secretary'). Aligns with professionalAvailabilities.jobTypes.
Indexed: Yes.
startTime: Timestamp
Description: The exact date and time when the work shift/period begins (UTC).
Indexed: Yes.
endTime: Timestamp
Description: The exact date and time when the work shift/period ends (UTC).
Indexed: Yes.
location: Map
Description: The specific physical location where the work needs to be performed.
Fields:
address: Map ({ street, number, postalCode, city, canton, country: 'CH' })
locationName: String (Optional, e.g., "Main Dispensary", "Ward 3 East")
Indexed: Yes (on canton, potentially postalCode).
description: String (Optional)
Description: Detailed information about the tasks, responsibilities, and context.
requiredSkills: Array&lt;String> (Optional)
Description: List of specific skills or certifications needed (e.g., ['BLS_certified', 'french_c1', 'system_X_proficient']).
Indexed: Yes (Array contains).
compensation: Map
Description: Details about the offered payment.
Fields:
type: String Enum ('hourly', 'fixed_for_shift')
grossAmount: Number
currency: String ('CHF')
notes: String (Optional, e.g., "Includes public holiday bonus")
applicants: Array&lt;Map> (Optional)
Description: List of professionals who have applied or been shortlisted for this need. Consider a subcollection applications if this list can become very large.
Fields (per applicant):
professionalProfileId: String
userId: String
applicationTimestamp: Timestamp
status: String Enum ('applied', 'shortlisted', 'rejected', 'assigned')
assignedProfessional: Map (Optional, populated when status is 'filled')
Description: Details of the professional assigned to this need.
Fields:
professionalProfileId: String
userId: String
assignmentTimestamp: Timestamp
generatedContractId: String (Optional)
Description: Reference to a formal contracts document if one was created specifically for this need/assignment.
internalReference: String (Optional)
Description: An identifier used by the employer for their internal tracking.
createdAt: Timestamp
Description: When this need record was created.
lastUpdatedAt: Timestamp
Description: When this need record was last modified.
expiryDate: Timestamp (Optional)
Description: Date after which this need should automatically become 'expired' if not filled or cancelled.
